==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sarcophaga
<hw>Sar*coph"a*ga</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
neut. pl. See <er>Sarcophagus</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
suborder of carnivorous and insectivorous marsupials including the
dasyures and the opossums.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sarcophaga</ent>⟦br⟧
