==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sarcophaga
<hw>Sar*coph"a*ga</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fem. sing. See
<er>Sarcophagus</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of Diptera,
including the flesh flies.</def>⟦br⟧
